title: NFL Storylines  We're Overly Invested In
itunes:title: NFL Storylines  We're Overly Invested In
description:
A room filled with heroes- Dan Hanzus, Chris Wesseling, Marc Sessler and Gregg Rosenthal bring you all the latest news around the NFL including Joe Flacco getting all the 1st team reps for the Broncos (8:38) and Chris Harris staying with the team. (12:20) Aaron Rodgers may have appeared in Game Of Thrones, but in there are more signs of dysfunction in Green Bay on the football front (14:03). Sadly, former Chiefs coach Gunther Cunningham has died at 72 (23:03). The heroes then share the NFL storylines that they're overly invested in. (30:20)
